Interface IPublicRole

All Superinterfaces:
IRole
All Known Subinterfaces:
IDatabaseAdministrator, ILogger
All Known Implementing Classes:
DatabaseAdministrator, LoggerRole
public interface IPublicRole
extends IRole

This interface is used to tag a role as public, that is a role that must have a public part that will be weaved/transferred to the agent proxy.
